Online Learning Management System
This project is an Online Learning Management System built using .NET 8 MVC and MySQL. The application allows administrators and users to manage courses, modules, quizzes, and questions.

Features
User Management: Create, read, update, and delete user information with roles (Admin, Student).
Course Management: Admins can create and manage courses.
Module Management: Admins can add and manage modules within courses.
Quiz Management: Admins can create quizzes for each course module.
Question Management: Admins can add questions to quizzes with multiple choice options.
Authentication and Authorization: Role-based access control to ensure only admins can perform certain actions.
Technologies Used
.NET 8 MVC: For building the web application.
MySQL: As the database for storing application data.
Entity Framework Core: For database interactions.
Bootstrap: For responsive UI design.
